{"tid":969414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗派艦隊赴大西洋向美示威","createTime":"2019-01-05T04:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T04:59:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"139b1e08d2c58b9a959d65b8e9ec31820572b0c3","tid":969414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190105/20584207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F20584207&d=T1%2FbvXP8%2Bo0cJI4QM9OX2%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=027855c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F20584207&h=2fec0e7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190105/20584207</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月05日 <br />\n<br />\n伊朗派艦隊赴大西洋向美示威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190105/large/iran.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190105%2Flarge%2Firan.jpg&h=dada9aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊朗海軍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍核動力航母「斯坦尼斯號」戰鬥群上月駛入波斯灣，向伊朗施加更大的軍事壓力後，德黑蘭決定以眼還眼，昨日宣佈將派一支艦隊到大西洋的美國後花園展示實力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月出發　包括導彈驅逐艦<br />\n<br />\n伊朗海軍副司令哈桑尼表示，包括集海陸空攻擊能力的新型導彈驅逐艦「薩汗德號」（Sahand）在內的小型艦隊，將會在今年3月遠赴大西洋，執行為期五個月的任務。<br />\n<br />\n哈桑尼說：「通過持續在國際水域出現，伊朗海軍履行了最高領袖的命令，揚起伊斯蘭共和國的旗幟，挫敗反伊朗的陰謀，保障航線安全。」哈桑尼上月曾透露，由兩至三艘戰艦組成的遠航艦隊，將會以委內瑞拉為目的地。<br />\n<br />\n自從去年5月美國總統特朗普撕毀核協議，重新嚴厲制裁伊朗後，美伊關係急轉直下。伊朗認為，既然美軍已在家門口耀武揚威，他們也有權派軍艦到大西洋接近美國的水域巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n近年，伊朗不遺餘力發展遠洋海軍，早在2014年便首次派戰艦到大西洋執勤，其後以打擊海盜為名，出兵印度洋和亞丁灣保護伊朗商船。近幾年，伊朗軍艦更常常出現在盟友敍利亞的領海。<br />\n<br />\n路透社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n逾半保守黨員寧願無協議脫歐"},{"pid":"6764e7c15e162c5b89bef42b6f32578a3312688f","tid":969414,"uid":27553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:52:20.000Z","msg":"示弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8487b66dde67e8ddaa65b0cf49b651b147f92f","tid":969414,"uid":191352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3674e7d4a9e89c9f3b4e5b8bc655cd7c1397dd3c","tid":969414,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f554b7b47e608d383f99e1754d017b531fa7447a","tid":969414,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6764e7c15e162c5b89bef42b6f32578a3312688f","tid":969414,"uid":27553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:52:20.000Z","msg":"示弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"中共連示弱都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6ae59463b7a1771636038a97544bea36a0422c","tid":969414,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3674e7d4a9e89c9f3b4e5b8bc655cd7c1397dd3c","tid":969414,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:54:17.000Z","msg":"會唔會頂唔住大西洋沉咗"},{"pid":"11a0f3c790c5a8343426d9b62571d8af371ce511","tid":969414,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"要構成到威脅先叫示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24c8031a7d4eae7a00a0ad2565728ac0749ec25","tid":969414,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"爛船一架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid